Stock management

How to manage product ordering when out of stock
OUT_OF_STOCK_NO_ORDER : Refuse order when out of stock
OUT_OF_STOCK_ACCEPT_ORDER : Accept the orders when out of stock
OUT_OF_STOCK_DEFAULT : Default webshop config behaviour when out of stock

Stock quantity management

DEPENDS_ON_STOCK_MANUAL : Manual management of quantities from product sheet..
